        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Domestic Terrorism Penalties Act of 2019</b></p> <p>This bill addresses domestic terrorism by establishing criminal penalties for murder, assault, and other specified crimes when they are committed with the intent to (1) intimidate or coerce a civilian population; or (2) influence, affect, or retaliate against the conduct or policy of a government.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
